TEXT runtimeÂ·asmstdcall(SB),NOSPLIT,$0
	MOVL	c+0(FP), BX

	// SetLastError(0).
	MOVL	$0, 0x34(FS)

	// Copy args to the stack.
	MOVL	SP, BP

	RET
